summary: 6 texture change options for the UNP SFW Bikini.
descriptionHtml:
This mod includes 6 texture change options for the SFW Bikinis for UNP Main Body or Skinny Body/UNPB SFW bikini. The patterns are Hearts,Vintage,Rainbow Glitter,Colored Spots,Tiger Print,and Leather.

Manual Install Only.
